column4: OK, i got the flashplayer to at least work, but now I get this error message: "the video you are trying to watch is currently unavailable. please check back soon."
anyone deal with this on jaunty?
can anyone help me with flashplayer 10 error messages?

i am trying to view videos on theberrics.com and it keeps saying "The video you are trying to watch is unavailable. Check back soon" it has been saying this for weeks. I've tried open source flashplayers, regular flashplayers, updating... everything
that's an error msg from the site not from flashplayer
